{"tid":2303373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[陳7入決賽啦] [29/11 4pm截止投票] 明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸 (5)","createTime":"2020-11-28T01:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T00:17:27.000Z","uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f868e34cddc96670be2ea9d45db0a78ff6f9386","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"Post 1:<br />\n明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2272221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2272221</a><br />\n<br />\nPost 2:<br />\n明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2285299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2285299</a><br />\n<br />\nPost 3:<br />\n明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸 (3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2290310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2290310</a><br />\n<br />\nPost 4:<br />\n[陳7入決賽啦] 明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸 (4)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aFMNiMU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aFMNiMU</a><br />\n<br />\n上次四強全靠大家先推到🇭🇰陳肇麒入決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次又要大家幫手了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對手係馬爾代夫仔，截止時間係<strong><span class=\"red\">29/11 4pm</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>背景資料:</strong></span></span><br />\n亞洲足協搞左個「歷屆亞協盃金球選舉」，入圍球員包括前🇭🇰國腳陳肇麒同林嘉緯<br />\n當中陳7已經成功殺入決賽，林嘉緯就八強止步<br />\n*亞協盃係一項亞洲球會級足球賽，過往南華同傑志都殺入過四強<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>投票形勢:</strong></span></span><br />\n截至2020-11-28 09:51<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOoe905.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOoe905.png&h=7d84b1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>投票方法:</strong></span></span><br />\n去下面條link，碌落d就見到投票option，click 'Chan Siu Ki' 就完成投票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/latest/news/afc-cup-bracket-challenge-final-ali-ashfaq-new-radiant-vs-chan-siu-ki-south-chin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-afc.com%2Fcompetitions%2Fafc-cup%2Flatest%2Fnews%2Fafc-cup-bracket-challenge-final-ali-ashfaq-new-radiant-vs-chan-siu-ki-south-chin&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=9dc2b00b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/latest/news/afc-cup-bracket-challenge-final-ali-ashfaq-new-radiant-vs-chan-siu-ki-south-chin</a><br />\n<br />\n因為原理咁簡陋，只要轉個browser或者用無痕模式就可以投多次，對手要洗票可謂毫無難度...<br />\n<br />\n一部電話每次係可以投15票up<br />\nSafari<br />\nSafari無痕<br />\nChrome<br />\nChrome無痕<br />\nFirefox<br />\nFirefox無痕<br />\nOpera<br />\nOpera無痕<br />\nFacebook 內置browser<br />\nIG 內置browser<br />\nTG 內置browser<br />\nTwitter 內置browser<br />\n連登內置browser<br />\nFb Messenger 內置browser<br />\nSkype 內置browser"},{"pid":"9af8960affe67e57aec0faaca0fec05da9366859","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"我諗實有人問「點解咁執著於呢d打飛機投票」<br />\n或者講「對面嗰球係靚d喎」<br />\n其實講到尾<br />\n我地都係想香港足球重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩假波新聞、足總垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、球會退賽<br />\n身為香港波球迷完全控制唔到<br />\n我地能力範圍內就只可以入場打氣、網上投票，為香港足球爭取正面曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2018年亞冠盃(比亞協盃再高一級既比賽)<br />\n同樣有金球投票<br />\n當時全靠球迷投票，🇭🇰香港球員鄭展龍先拎到每週及年度金球<br />\n帶來既除左個人名銜，仲有唔同媒體既報導<br />\n包括亞洲足協官方訪問<br />\n個人/球會背後商業得益/marketing效果我地量化唔到<br />\n但最起碼係由我地球迷創造左呢個機會出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以希望今次亞協盃金球選舉<br />\n陳7入到決賽<br />\n終極目標係順利拎到冠軍！！<br />\n希望大家投投票，比個機會香港足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IiDcNp47-gA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIiDcNp47-gA&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=636b95eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IiDcNp47-gA</a>"},{"pid":"a0fca7af03c23733237418a5651453d5b85cb322","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"關於亞協盃金球投票<br />\n有個問題困擾好耐<br />\n就係點樣有效地投票...<br />\n<br />\n之前寫過一d心得<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n1. 用電話network<br />\n2. 用電話browser<br />\n3. 登入左google account<br />\n4. 唔用VPN<br />\n5. 每投完一票清cookies<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n依家可以加多樣<br />\n就係「經唔同社交媒體帖文，轉折地進入投票網站」<br />\n咁可能通過到投票網站背後既reCAPTCHA v3驗證<br />\n從而成功投票<br />\n<br />\n大家盡力一試💪<br />\nFrom: 數字球"},{"pid":"3b4d5c7eed45234c6dbc4c0605c6723b733f1ac0","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"陳7要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f346552a03b1b4cb08966bc3475ae193b01158","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501991f9884f12a8ecdc6ca95a1bd7908b5a18fa","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c3bafb3acd053f7722cb2d422acaa4f70dcdb7","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32aee3e2ced7e844bc9e05511efed0c91175646","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8e22b4ca7b0013e889d30634df86e3821ee297","tid":2303373,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11